{"tid":313572,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[魔獸世界]Warmane Icecrown","createTime":"2017-07-08T12:33:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T07:51:23.000Z","uid":73938,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"32a51b7cb03dbc3a41e33a44b07c121dc5189d0f","tid":313572,"uid":73938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T12:33:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">仲記得以前打副本嘅日子?</span><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/08/200809_3fb2db6cccf4a23383383394b28b2b31.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F08%2F200809_3fb2db6cccf4a23383383394b28b2b31.jpg&h=19a2e048&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">仲記唔記得呢個係邊個?</span><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/08/200856_0873d5754908ff32f7e251055e65b130.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F08%2F200856_0873d5754908ff32f7e251055e65b130.jpg&h=0a96413f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔記得唔緊要<br />\n<br />\n以前巫妖王版本已經過去<br />\n但有鬼佬開左個私服係巫妖王版本<br />\n平均每日有12K+人上線 唔再驚私服冇人玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁執粒呢? 放心 唔需要擔心執粒 因為呢個伺服器有贊助功能 贊助亦能獲得網站點數買自己心水裝備 直升滿lv都冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n(離左題)<br />\n放心 伺服器已經穩定運行達7年以上 而且Icecrown版本有7倍經 唔會升得過快或過慢 而且其餘遊戲設置全同官服一樣 可以體驗遊戲樂趣  唔會話一開始無敵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以就算玩過當回憶 亦話因為自己細細個冇錢玩唔起 宜家都可以玩返!<br />\n<br />\n咁下載地址 ( 上一個post 樓主用官網下載嘅BT 有D慢 對我地黎講 用返Google download 當然會快啲 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/0B1PMTqz8Q3oiLTlNQnZPbmNtakE/view\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F0B1PMTqz8Q3oiLTlNQnZPbmNtakE%2Fview&d=IFSoehw9b4HQe4nYzidLpU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=7ccc664c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/file/d/0B1PMTqz8Q3oiLTlNQnZPbmNtakE/view</a><br />\n<br />\n合共18GB左右<br />\n<br />\n其次 註冊帳號<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.warmane.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.warmane.com&d=IFSoehw9b4HQe4nYzidLpU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=97ade871\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.warmane.com</a><br />\n<br />\n註冊完 download完仲差幾步就玩得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n首先解壓-&gt;再去主目錄搵Data嘅File -&gt; 搵zhTW嘅File -&gt; 用txt檔開realmlist-&gt;改做SET realmlist &quot;<a href=\"http://logon.warmane.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flogon.warmane.com&d=IFSoehw9b4HQe4nYzidLpU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=c6ae078b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">logon.warmane.com</a>&quot; <br />\n<br />\n跟住去返主目錄 開Game再Login 選擇Icecrown 伺服器就玩得!<br />\n<br />\nSorry 第一次出文 可能冇咩圖 有啲悶 字打錯請屌得細力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n小弟玩部落盜賊 已經滿Lv 但我入嘅唔係香港人公會 如有香港人公會請通知(呢個ser有得轉陣型 唔洗擔心 e.g 部落轉聯盟) 所以有香港人搞公會 請邀我入埋黎Happy<br />\n<br />\n如果入game有顯示咩你所登錄語音同伺服器唔同 定唔知咩<br />\n請download一下Bat檔放入主目錄 開啟<br />\n開左=開game 之後就應該冇事<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=0ByaZD-JCOHVOQ2VSc2lpblFheEU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D0ByaZD-JCOHVOQ2VSc2lpblFheEU&d=IFSoehw9b4HQe4nYzidLpU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=7ea3bc17\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=0ByaZD-JCOHVOQ2VSc2lpblFheEU</a><br />\n<br />\n如果驚有毒定咩 可以先編輯睇下內容 放心 唔會玩各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我Game名叫Kzplzg<br />\nRC群:27664006 掛住係入面先 有咩問我"},{"pid":"aa62d5f3600ee3b380355601c1b6ec1d5224428e","tid":313572,"uid":103497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T17:32:58.000Z","msg":"想問下...UI個到係未都可以用番以前大腳個啲?"},{"pid":"6ad2e0c0eaf990ec994c9edfa7c3353e81ff7922","tid":313572,"uid":37240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T18:45:29.0